         When you get right down to it, the whole idea of 'camping out' to avoid a full wipeout on a raid is an exploit.  It's a situation of taking advantage of the limitations of the gaming environment to maximize the abilities of the players.  Why not introduce something like a targettable FD to provide an alternative to this strategy???  I think it's a reasonable suggestion and has descent merit.</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
